So pass TWO filtered lists to the canvas:
- `visiblePreviewEvents` (pending + accepted, for ghost well rendering)
  — filters out rejected
- `badgePreviewEvents` (all, for badge rendering) — no filter on state,
  only on labware

Render `<PreviewEventBadges>` with `badgePreviewEvents` and pass it to
LabwareCanvas via the new `previewEventBadges` prop.

Pass `previewEventStates` and `setPreviewEventState` through the prop
chain from `LabwareEventEditor.tsx` → `DualLabwarePane` →
